<div class="title">Anaesthetic Hypothermia</div>
<div class="substance">Bupropion, Dextroamphetamine & Cannabis</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Curious&Exact=1">Curious</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Curious. "Anaesthetic Hypothermia: An Experience with Bupropion, Dextroamphetamine & Cannabis (exp76532)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 21, 2013. erowid.org/exp/76532</div>

